{"tid":602774,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大家以為得鄭金鈴先係新移民既表表者？","createTime":"2018-03-23T08:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T14:05:54.000Z","uid":49169,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"72fc721508c78f8ad95404c9dd487c13bdef9047","tid":602774,"uid":49169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:06:42.000Z","msg":"見到咁多人都係到狙擊阿金鈴我覺得你地真係好撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話晒人地都係努力上進水人丫係咪先，搵食姐，犯法呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就好似我大學同學呢位阿冰冰咁，作為一位支那人就真係幾撚努力。含管畢業做咩好？梗係努力賣保險啦屌你老味，最重要係幫到客人丫嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/051558_cb94a801f2dc0d8a16b3f821831aa099.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F051558_cb94a801f2dc0d8a16b3f821831aa099.png&h=292a0eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拿我大飛份人就最公道既，阿冰冰作為一隻保證狗都算幾食腦。當一般既保險狗仲停留係facebook打飛機既時候，阿冰冰已經諗到搵人寫膳稿一齊打飛機，威撚到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/051908_34ff947f57550618bba6c19edb971b53.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F051908_34ff947f57550618bba6c19edb971b53.png&h=228be1b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為一個支那人，奶下共都係好撚合理既事丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/052054_9956889c3759fe1af8f2b5b8bdc7697c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F052054_9956889c3759fe1af8f2b5b8bdc7697c.png&h=a9cdfb97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為一隻保險狗，識玩一定係玩埋扮韓妹賣化妝品食埋港女條水<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/052303_b5f38bf0aeea9d6c30ef0ed8e074ab4f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F052303_b5f38bf0aeea9d6c30ef0ed8e074ab4f.png&h=5ef88744&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/052336_44a8c09a9533cae6068e311a2b4ec86b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F052336_44a8c09a9533cae6068e311a2b4ec86b.png&h=c471c2ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/052347_7d0a4f1a96c574074968dcdebf300e42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F052347_7d0a4f1a96c574074968dcdebf300e42.png&h=a28c5da1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嘩屌你講痴講厚臉皮咁撚勁，不如侵侵搵佢去研究下一代既避彈衣啦屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過就咁，我呀大飛份人就真係好撚公道既。阿冰冰作為一個支那人都支持港獨台獨，呢個就真係值得尊重呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/052735_afbcf6eac80f3b67c8d3ba0c73d462d1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F052735_afbcf6eac80f3b67c8d3ba0c73d462d1.png&h=f3ce4582&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cab70b3ea4b6ce42b689b6f64398250b5cbd54c6","tid":602774,"uid":35046,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:16:27.000Z","msg":"條女好撚樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452872343177ffca120385d6ca76e6acb129ea16","tid":602774,"uid":49169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:25:23.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cefe391f09f1a275bbae732ceff2a2ebd848abb5","tid":602774,"uid":9651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cab70b3ea4b6ce42b689b6f64398250b5cbd54c6","tid":602774,"uid":35046,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:16:27.000Z","msg":"條女好撚樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:36:51.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a909e919c1f7261121bc6caed0c47f6c5c690cc","tid":602774,"uid":78815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T09:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f137169856d7bb6a0770b4a63021b6d79a13dfb7","tid":602774,"uid":49169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27719c8c1af11e75fbbdba5d99bd6211921a3532","tid":602774,"uid":4239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:24:33.000Z","msg":"要求DQ阿，4個國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f664a36c5076174ddca1a1c2f5d2e6e615a2c2f","tid":602774,"uid":109386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:32:52.000Z","msg":"邊撚個？唔識"},{"pid":"8426876b2219da37b33fdcab8200920db7ff2dc7","tid":602774,"uid":49169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27719c8c1af11e75fbbdba5d99bd6211921a3532","tid":602774,"uid":4239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:24:33.000Z","msg":"要求DQ阿，4個國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T11:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8af3b3b27e93a99f21153bd65f3db86bee67da1","tid":602774,"uid":130405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T18:21:47.000Z","msg":"支那雞 保險狗"},{"pid":"20779c1dc1801c8477a46a488780177c9d1d9187","tid":602774,"uid":36077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T18:23:44.000Z","msg":"大飛<br />\n識唔識印鹹書呀？"},{"pid":"ae7bac1977153364c913f35224b985200ceb9f57","tid":602774,"uid":59487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T13:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/163316_1b3d0883cb7e2c729b78da33fe9b9419.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F163316_1b3d0883cb7e2c729b78da33fe9b9419.jpg&h=9a72bc1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4790443e4ee02cd7191efb17b642449541d105a","tid":602774,"uid":29773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:42:03.000Z","msg":"乜水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我淨係識三國o個個甘寧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840a645ec04d1eab3aee5679ce83367b5b01893e","tid":602774,"uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:15:11.000Z","msg":"借刀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14a3e8d2fdb54a8394aef73ac17b709b757c5c2","tid":602774,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:19:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借刀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識唔識借刀點解？"},{"pid":"c6310012ab2a6f1dc16e1ca3fe412a55eec8f6e0","tid":602774,"uid":2471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b14a3e8d2fdb54a8394aef73ac17b709b757c5c2","tid":602774,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:19:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借刀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識唔識借刀點解？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:26:22.000Z","msg":"借刀，網民術語，原是高登討論區用詞之一，意思即借刀殺人。它是指網民利用網絡社群、其他網民甚至傳統傳媒陷害目標人物，令目標人物無論在名譽或財富等均有所損失。<br />\n<br />\n借刀文化與起底文化也是息息相關。真亦假時假亦真，有人利用「起底」達成「借刀」目的，意即借刀殺人，把仇人的資料包裝成自己的資料，再假扮被起底，借起底人士之力打擊仇人。<br />\n<br />\n因為借刀行為在網上討論區時有發生，而且高登討論區廣為人知，所以借刀一詞亦散播開去，廣為各大討論區、網誌等社交網站、甚至是報章雜誌等傳統傳媒使用。<br />\n<br />\n借刀行為層出不窮，網民等各類人士若不加以小心查證，很易中招：<br />\n<br />\n利用別人名字進行斷jer（打賭）行為，引來別人攻擊目標人物；成功後燒jer（設局毀譽），讓目標人物留下污名。<br />\n在其他討論區冒充別人的名字註冊會員，及後做出違反討論區規則的行為，以達到抹黑他人的目的。<br />\n會員在「會員自貼區」自貼，但貼的不是貼他自己，而是他的目標，跟著做犯眾憎的行為，令其他會員群起攻擊他的目標。<br />\n把目標人物的相片貼上討論區，然後意圖發起網民恥笑，希望靠網友之力，把圖片宣揚開去。但此等圖謀通常很快會被拆穿，無法成事，部份更可能反被網民起底。<br />\n假扮起底成功，實則貼出的是敵人的資料。有時敵人與當事人相似，令到其他網友深信不疑，其中一單證實借刀成功的例子是2008年網民亂指大學生為強姦案疑犯事件<br />\n在香港網絡大典刻意抹黑他人，寫壞別人的名聲，卻沒有附上或選擇性附上可供查證的資料來源。<br />\n有些愛以起底及批鬥為樂的人，為了令有關人物的起底資料合理化，因而作出炒作，製造「公眾利益」的假象，令其推到上報，之後那受害者就會變成了「公眾人物」，那就為借刀人士提供了一個一條龍式的上位途徑，令網上欺凌合理化，實情為道德綁架。 [1]"},{"pid":"64a635ff3077d7fc6e9e2a49226c3bffbdc14658","tid":602774,"uid":113516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b14a3e8d2fdb54a8394aef73ac17b709b757c5c2","tid":602774,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:19:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借刀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識唔識借刀點解？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:35:56.000Z","msg":"咁樓主借鄭金鈴個名再post個自己唔鍾意既人上黎做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大把內地人做保險狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a86b370565c73ad058df019935936a52873c0f2","tid":602774,"uid":161322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T13:08:03.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢大學同學呀 含管咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e5638e487b6ee143f98b0f0a2a0a5c1a14e913","tid":602774,"uid":47055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T14:00:40.000Z","msg":"豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a826b6c8bb82ad00306e3b17bce703d118ba31c","tid":602774,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T14:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc14d1b529604440f1afe93f956f0ca1ab96973","tid":602774,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T14:05:54.000Z","msg":"有乜撚野好Po? <br />\n私人恩怨死返facebook啦 死5p狗"}]}